data.description: Get ready, The Sandcastle in La Selva Beach is on the market for the 1st time ever ! Aptly named as it sits above the shores below. Providing sweeping panoramic whitewater views of the Monterey Bay, with miles of open space vistas. This is possibly the most peaceful oceanside location along the Coast. A destination of tranquility with access to miles of beach and no crowds.  Deeply loved and enjoyed by this family for years. Now its your turn for the next chapter. Plenty of space 4 bedrooms, 2 sunrooms,2 car garage  with ocean views from almost every room. Built in 1972 on a private lane away from the hustle and bustle of life.
